1. Install tool chain from scratch (https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/get-started/linux-setup.html)
2. Check which version of IDF and IDF-Arduino are compatible (check for the keyword IDF in IDF Arduino commit to see the latest supported version)
3. Get the correct version of IDF
4. Install the Arduino components (https://github.com/espressif/arduino-esp32) in the directory components
5. Install esp32-camera (https://github.com/espressif/esp32-camera) components in the directory components

Compile project with idf.py build
Flash with idf.py flash

